text: Jeannot Welter was a boxer from Luxembourg. Welter competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. He was born on 15 March 1928 and died on 22 December 1998.Jeannot Welter == References == Category:1928 births Category:1998 deaths Category:Luxembourgian boxers Category:Olympians for Luxembourg
